{
  "stem": "21308.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But, Vincent was my Christian Jew I told you about.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he used to join us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He was a good chap.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "A very good officer.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, on the first day, it was very difficult.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Very difficult.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because-- well, we weren't trained for it, as you can well imagine.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It was very easy to blow one's top.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we had to establish law and order.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was absolutely determined that in that camp, the British law and order would reign.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now, the Russians, for instance, didn't see it that way.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They wanted an independent Russia in the camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I said, no, you won't have it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they had an appointed head.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there was only going to be one law and order there and that was British.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that was fair to everybody, including the Germans.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And-- as I insisted that that was it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I was very wise, in retrospect, to have done it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because it curtailed people from settling things their own way.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we-- we had trouble.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I mean, we-- the Russians decided they were going to fillet one bloak alive, who they said had been collaborating.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he was brought into my office.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the skin on his back was hanging down.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They were filleting him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And that was one of their own people, mind you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And anyway, we bundled him off to hospital and created hell with the leader.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I gave him the drubbing he would never forget.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But he was a good chap.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "He was a-- a Russian tank corps officer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Very good chap.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But when he-- when he realized that I wasn't going to stand for it, he supported me all the way down the road.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Until we got a Russian LO appointed in.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
